                <h1>DEMAN weekend offers gateway to media world</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/f7f25f2e-4b36-4963-ba14-50f1028763fc.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;DEMAN&#x20;Arts&#x20;&amp;&#x20;Media&#x20;Weekend&#x20;offers&#x20;two&#x20;full&#x20;days&#x20;of&#x20;workshops&#x20;and&#x20;dialogue&#x20;with&#x20;accomplished&#x20;Duke&#x20;alumni.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>DEMAN Arts & Media Weekend offers two full days of workshops and dialogue with accomplished Duke alumni.&nbsp;</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/will-atkinson">Will Atkinson</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">November 9, 2016 | 12:00am EST</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
